metadata.name: Detection (Red diagonal strip)
metadata.description:
Film , analog multiexposure,
digital scan, 2250 x 3372 px.,
2013 y.

In my photos of buildings, streets, malls
I share my personal analysis and research.
By finding key features of the architectural
volume I create a new architectural objects
that hover in the air and have a different interpretation in urban space.
I often use the technique of symmetry and call it a variant of unwrapping (bending) perspective.
